{"tid":2197470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"使用飛機杯的正確施展力方法","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T04:48:32.000Z","uid":105678,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"baa472d7b234c5fce64408ef2c3a6cc1b2ac4676","tid":2197470,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"近日多左朋友PM我詢問有關於使用飛機杯後下肢出現疼痛、如廁滴水嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n作為一名泌尿科專家，希望廣大男性都了解正確的方法使用飛機杯，避開風險動作，建立幸福賓周社會。<br />\n<br />\n首先講下最常見嘅錯誤施力方式：單手夾緊<br />\n<br />\n何謂夾緊，請見下圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE65rUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE65rUs.jpg&h=36ce11e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即為追求最大快感將飛機杯當係握力器起勢咁揸，當自己細佬係仇人咁上chok下chok，再加上✈️杯本身緊繃嘅特性，難免傷到下肢。<br />\n<br />\n大家要知道細佬只係海綿體，冇肌肉咁結實，好易受傷的...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuQqrWg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuQqrWg.jpg&h=edcd8ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下來想入正題，講下正確打飛機嘅關鍵：兩手並用<br />\n<br />\n使用飛機杯時係腦內觀想太極圖，想像太初之始、一陰一陽嘅極端力量。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，保持腹式呼吸，一呼一吐，慣用手握住飛機杯，並用另一隻包住喺外圍作為輔助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HtrVRU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HtrVRU.gif&h=9951e170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成以上準備動作，即可以輔助手為主，輕輕chok你嘅飛機杯，切記慣用手唔好出一絲一毫力量。<br />\n<br />\n即係混用坊間俗稱嘅陰力！<br />\n<br />\n同時唔好中斷腹式呼吸，專注專注再專注！<br />\n<br />\n然後你會感受到來自下肢嘅喜悅，感覺唔夠唔緊要，請用輔助手再增添摩擦，細水長流，喜由心生。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候你已經與細佬不分你我，融為一體，成為幸福賓周了～"},{"pid":"c945641c42fe3b49780aa6a2f6009bc91792dc19","tid":2197470,"uid":133714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b672b5ba0c714fc2c7c8af39e6e33058d70eda","tid":2197470,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會太勁"},{"pid":"834e02e2933ac37caebcf011cbf5f7f8c44c9a9f","tid":2197470,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"唔用飛機杯，咁要點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4daaeb15e2902d9d4b684cd9fc53d2fe46da37","tid":2197470,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c945641c42fe3b49780aa6a2f6009bc91792dc19","tid":2197470,"uid":133714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"希望幫到大家～"},{"pid":"d75e777166720a7b7d60701ee15e8446707d347a","tid":2197470,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"834e02e2933ac37caebcf011cbf5f7f8c44c9a9f","tid":2197470,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"唔用飛機杯，咁要點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"最緊要係陰力，其次係意志力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e708578f6b178de327dbbad3e0bf9c30b0cf1215","tid":2197470,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fc4daaeb15e2902d9d4b684cd9fc53d2fe46da37","tid":2197470,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c945641c42fe3b49780aa6a2f6009bc91792dc19","tid":2197470,"uid":133714,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"希望幫到大家～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:38:34.000Z","msg":"不生受用.............<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de47529e59d5652f42b2c5edf82e81